# eof-line-string

## Input

```
key hello world
```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..15
  ENTRY@0..15
    WORD_KEY@0..3
      WORD@0..3 "key"
    SPACE@3..4 " "
    LINE_STRING@4..15
      STRING@4..15 "hello world"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..3 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@4..15 "hello world",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

